#: src/security/tool-receipts.md:49
msgid "What receipts don't prevent"
msgstr ""

#: src/security/tool-receipts.md:51
msgid ""
"The LLM can still say anything in its text output — receipts don't suppress "
"responses."
msgstr ""

#: src/security/tool-receipts.md:52
msgid ""
"The LLM can answer questions without using tools at all. Receipts only "
"verify tool calls that were made, not tool calls that should have been made."
msgstr ""

