#: src/reference/sop/connectivity.md:97
msgid "4. Cron Integration"
msgstr ""

#: src/reference/sop/connectivity.md:99
msgid ""
"The scheduler evaluates cached cron triggers using a window-based check."
msgstr ""

#: src/reference/sop/connectivity.md:101
msgid "**Window-based:** events within `(last_check, now]` are not missed."
msgstr ""

#: src/reference/sop/connectivity.md:102
msgid ""
"**At-most-once per expression per tick:** if multiple fire points are in one "
"poll window, dispatch happens once."
msgstr ""

#: src/reference/sop/connectivity.md:104
msgid "Trigger example:"
msgstr ""

#: src/reference/sop/connectivity.md:106
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"cron\"\n"
"expression = \"0 0 8 * * *\"\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/reference/sop/connectivity.md:112
msgid "Cron expressions support 5, 6, or 7 fields."
msgstr ""

